FILTERS IN EBIRDS
__________________

make pip
make diff_filters

To verify the Canar filter is working well:
make verify_filter

To get the infos:
https://review.ebird.org/admin/viewFilter.htm?checklistID=CL24828 => Save as active_filter.html
https://review.ebird.org/admin/viewFilter.htm?checklistID=CL34436 => Save as canar_filter.html

